487
00:43:50,220 --> 00:43:52,320
Transmission from the Klingon prison
planet, what exactly did it say?

488
00:43:52,420 --> 00:43:56,520
- Oh my God, what's wrong with your hands?
- Who is responsible for the Klingon attack?

489
00:43:56,720 --> 00:43:58,520
- Was the ship Romu...?
- Was the ship what?

490
00:43:59,320 --> 00:44:01,120
- What's happening to my mouth?
- You got numb tongue?

491
00:44:01,155 --> 00:44:03,320
- Numb tongue?!
- I can fix that.

492
00:44:03,420 --> 00:44:06,920
- Was the ship what?
- Romulan.

493
00:44:06,955 --> 00:44:08,320
- What?
- Romulan.

494
00:44:08,420 --> 00:44:09,420
- Romulan? - Yeah.
- Yes. - Yeah!

495
00:44:44,620 --> 00:44:48,020
Prod Nero seven Federation
ships are on their way.

496
00:44:50,220 --> 00:44:51,670
- Jim!
- What's going on?

497
00:44:51,705 --> 00:44:53,120
- Jim! Jim, come back.
- Captain!

498
00:44:53,520 --> 00:44:55,085
Captain Pike, sir, we have to stop the ship.

499
00:44:55,120 --> 00:44:57,520
Kirk, how the hell did you get
