00:45:18,620 --> 00:45:20,170
- I can remove the cadet...
- Try it!

510
00:45:20,205 --> 00:45:21,720
This cadet is trying to save the bridge!

511
00:45:21,820 --> 00:45:24,720
By recommending a full stop mid-warp
doing a rescue mission?

512
00:45:24,820 --> 00:45:26,520
It's not a rescue mission.
Listen to me. It's an attack.

513
00:45:26,555 --> 00:45:28,720
Based on what facts?

514
00:45:30,220 --> 00:45:33,220
That same anomaly,
a lightning storm in space

515
00:45:33,320 --> 00:45:35,220
that we saw today, also occurred
on the day of my birth.

516
00:45:35,320 --> 00:45:38,220
Before a Romulan ship attacked
the USS Kelvin.

517
00:45:38,320 --> 00:45:40,385
You know that, sir.
I've read your dissertation.

518
00:45:40,420 --> 00:45:42,920
That ship, which had formidable and
advanced weaponry

519
00:45:43,020 --> 00:45:44,820
was never seen or heard from again.

520
00:45:44,920 --> 00:45:46,920
The Kelvin attacked a place on
the edge of Klingon space.

521
00:45:46,955 --> 00:45:49,520
