- Sir, there's another Federation ship.
- Destroy it too.

549
00:47:50,920 --> 00:47:51,885
Fire torpedoes.

550
00:47:51,920 --> 00:47:53,085
Captain, they're locking torpedoes.

551
00:47:53,120 --> 00:47:55,820
Divert auxiliary power from port
nacelle to forward shields.

552
00:48:03,420 --> 00:48:05,985
- Sulu, status report.
- Shields at 32%.

553
00:48:06,020 --> 00:48:08,320
Their weapons are powerful, sir.
We can't take another hit like that.

554
00:48:08,420 --> 00:48:10,085
- Get me Starfleet command.
- Captain.

555
00:48:10,120 --> 00:48:12,920
The Romulan ship has lowered some
kind of high energy pulse device

556
00:48:13,020 --> 00:48:14,185
into the Vulcan atmosphere.

557
00:48:14,220 --> 00:48:17,020
