communications and transporter abilities.

558
00:48:17,120 --> 00:48:19,320
All power to forward shields.
Prepare to fire all weapons.

559
00:48:24,120 --> 00:48:25,220
Weapons ready.

560
00:48:25,620 --> 00:48:26,620
Wait!

561
00:48:27,220 --> 00:48:30,020
- The hull, magnify!
- Yes, sir.

562
00:48:34,620 --> 00:48:36,420
Captain, we're being hailed.

563
00:48:37,820 --> 00:48:40,020
Hello.

564
00:48:40,920 --> 00:48:43,120
I am the Captain Christopher Pike.
To whom am I speaking?

565
00:48:43,920 --> 00:48:45,420
Hi Christopher. I am Nero.

566
00:48:46,120 --> 00:48:48,620
You've declared war against the Federation.
Withdraw

567
