Romulan leadership at a neutral location.

568
00:48:52,020 --> 00:48:56,120
I do not speak for the Empire.
We stand apart.

569
00:48:57,620 --> 00:49:01,120
As does your Vulcan crew member.
Isn't that right, Spock?

570
00:49:04,020 --> 00:49:06,720
Pardon me, I do not believe that
you and I are acquainted.

571
00:49:07,020 --> 00:49:08,320
No, we're not.

572
00:49:08,620 --> 00:49:10,020
Not yet.

573
00:49:10,520 --> 00:49:13,520
Spock, there's something I
would like you to see.

574
00:49:15,320 --> 00:49:19,120
Captain Pike, your transporter
has been disabled.

575
00:49:19,520 --> 00:49:23,020
As you can see, by the rest of
the armada, you have no choice.

576
00:49:23,920 --> 00:49:27,820
You will man a shuttle. Come aboard
the Narada for negotiations.

577
00:49:28,620 --> 00:49:30,420
That is all.

578
00:49:39,220 --> 00:49:41,120
- Theyâll kill you, you know that.
