603
00:51:42,020 --> 00:51:44,085
It's not a prank, Spock.

604
00:51:44,120 --> 00:51:46,820
And I am not the captain, you are.

605
00:51:47,820 --> 00:51:49,220
Let's go.

606
00:51:51,720 --> 00:51:54,420
Sir, after we knock out that drill,
what happens to you?

607
00:51:54,520 --> 00:51:55,820
I guess you have to come and get me.

608
00:51:56,720 --> 00:51:59,320
Careful with the ship, Spock.
She's brand new.

609
00:52:10,620 --> 00:52:13,170
- Dr. Puri, report.
- It's McCoy.

610
00:52:13,205 --> 00:52:15,720
Doctor Puri was on deck 6.
He's dead.

611
00:52:17,020 --> 00:52:19,820
Then you have just inherited his
responsibility as chief medical officer.

612
00:52:19,920 --> 00:52:22,120
Yeah, tell me something I don't know.

